## Third-Party Data Notice

This repository includes the **Loughran-McDonald Master Dictionary 1993-2024**
at `data/reference/LoughranMcDonald_MasterDictionary.csv`. The dictionary is
distributed by the Software Repository for Accounting and Finance (SRAF) at
the University of Notre Dame and is licensed for non-commercial research use.

Citation: Loughran, T. and McDonald, B. (2011), "When Is a Liability Not a
Liability? Textual Analysis, Dictionaries, and 10-Ks," *Journal of Finance*,
66: 35-65.

If you use the LM dictionary in derivative work, please cite the above paper
and respect the SRAF non-commercial research license terms.
